        <mxCell id="HDKpm5i9qXrigkiqiV-I-1" value="&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Name&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;* when restart instance recieve event start from&amp;nbsp;following to event it proccessed before&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;* name define by &lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;tuple&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt; (instancename, source )&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;* &lt;b&gt;persist&lt;/b&gt; = true / farse&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;+ &lt;b&gt;true&lt;/b&gt; :&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- when all watcher disconnect, instance still hold,&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- watcher reconnect it receive new events since watcher disconnect&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- need commit log to store all event : send event, ack event&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;+ &lt;b&gt;false&lt;/b&gt; :&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- when all watcher disconnect , instance -&amp;gt; remove &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- when watcher reconnect , it&#39;ll have recieved event since it reconnect&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;*&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;multiWatcher&lt;/b&gt;=true/false&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;+ &lt;b&gt;true&lt;/b&gt; :&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- instance can hold multi watchers&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;+ &lt;b&gt;false&lt;/b&gt;:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- maximum number of watcher instance can hold is 1&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" vertex="1" parent="1">
