        <mxCell id="HDKpm5i9qXrigkiqiV-I-7" value="* jobs are stored in the order server has been recieving&lt;div&gt;* is a &lt;b&gt;circular array&lt;/b&gt; have a fix &lt;b&gt;max_size.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;* when queue evict it reject coming jobs&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" vertex="1" parent="1">
